  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Renal hypothermia may preserve renal function in patients who require partial nephrectomy. In
      preparation for a definitive randomized controlled trial this pilot study will assess
      feasibility and variance data to be used for sample size estimation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
